# src: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PtQiiknWUcI&t=1301s&ab_channel=TraversyMedia
1. clone full project for reference: `git clone https://github.com/divanov11/StudyBud.git` 
2. create virtual env: `python -m venv venv`
3. start your virtual env: `source venv/bin/activate`
4. install django: pip install django
5. run `django-admin`
6. get boilerplate for my project: `django-admin startproject <project_name>` -> project folder will be created
7. `cd <project_name>`
8. start django dev server: `python manage.py runserver`
9. create a app using django: `python manage.py startapp <app_name>` -> base folder will be created
10. django template engine